<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="light" lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>New Certification - Eco-Monolith</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script id="tailwind-config">
      tailwind.config = {
        darkMode: "class",
        theme: {
          extend: {
            "colors": {
                    "tertiary-fixed": "#ffd9dd",
                    "surface-container-low": "#f2f4f2",
                    "surface-variant": "#e1e3e1",
                    "on-secondary-fixed": "#390c00",
                    "tertiary": "#97344a",
                    "on-primary": "#ffffff",
                    "primary-container": "#15803d",
                    "background": "#f8faf8",
                    "on-error": "#ffffff",
                    "secondary-container": "#fd6b36",
                    "surface-container-lowest": "#ffffff",
                    "on-tertiary-container": "#fff1f1",
                    "outline": "#6f7a6e",
                    "surface-container": "#eceeec",
                    "on-tertiary": "#ffffff",
                    "tertiary-fixed-dim": "#ffb2bd",
                    "on-secondary-fixed-variant": "#832600",
                    "inverse-on-surface": "#eff1ef",
                    "on-error-container": "#93000a",
                    "tertiary-container": "#b64c62",
                    "surface-tint": "#006d30",
                    "error": "#ba1a1a",
                    "on-secondary-container": "#5d1900",
                    "outline-variant": "#becabc",
                    "surface-container-highest": "#e1e3e1",
                    "on-surface": "#191c1b",
                    "on-background": "#191c1b",
                    "secondary": "#ac3400",
                    "surface-bright": "#f8faf8",
                    "primary-fixed": "#95f8a7",
                    "on-primary-fixed-variant": "#005323",
                    "surface-dim": "#d8dad9",
                    "primary-fixed-dim": "#79db8d",
                    "on-tertiary-fixed": "#400013",
                    "inverse-primary": "#79db8d",
                    "surface-container-high": "#e6e9e7",
                    "secondary-fixed-dim": "#ffb59d",
                    "inverse-surface": "#2e3130",
                    "on-tertiary-fixed-variant": "#81233b",
                    "error-container": "#ffdad6",
                    "surface": "#f8faf8",
                    "on-surface-variant": "#3f493f",
                    "on-primary-fixed": "#00210a",
                    "on-secondary": "#ffffff",
                    "secondary-fixed": "#ffdbd0",
                    "on-primary-container": "#d3ffd5",
                    "primary": "#00652c"
            },
            "borderRadius": {
                    "DEFAULT": "0.125rem",
                    "lg": "0.25rem",
                    "xl": "0.5rem",
                    "full": "0.75rem"
            },
            "fontFamily": {
                    "headline": ["Inter"],
                    "body": ["Inter"],
                    "label": ["Inter"]
            }
          },
        },
      }
    </script>
<style>
        .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .step-active { color: #ac3400; }
        .step-complete { color: #00652c; }
        .glass-panel {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-surface font-body text-on-surface antialiased">
<aside class="h-screen w-64 fixed left-0 top-0 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-950 flex flex-col p-6 space-y-8 z-40">
<div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">eco</span>
</div>
<div>
<h1 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-900 dark:text-emerald-50 leading-none">The Precise Monolith</h1>
<p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-800/60 mt-1">Energy Certification v1.0</p>
</div>
</div>
<nav class="flex-1 space-y-2">
<a class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 text-emerald-800/60 hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-all rounded-lg" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">dashboard</span>
<span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Dashboard</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-500 font-bold bg-white dark:bg-emerald-900 rounded-lg shadow-sm" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">verified</span>
<span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Certificates</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 text-emerald-800/60 hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-all rounded-lg" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">analytics</span>
<span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Reports</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 text-emerald-800/60 hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-all rounded-lg" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">settings</span>
<span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Settings</span>
</a>
</nav>
<div class="pt-6 border-t border-emerald-100/50 space-y-2">
<a class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 text-emerald-800/60 hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-all rounded-lg" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">help</span>
<span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Help Center</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 text-emerald-800/60 hover:bg-emerald-100 transition-all rounded-lg" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">logout</span>
<span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Logout</span>
</a>
</div>
</aside>
<main class="ml-64 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
<header class="w-full sticky top-0 z-30 flex justify-between items-center px-12 py-8 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md">
<div>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-emerald-900">New Energy Certificate</h2>
<div class="flex items-center mt-1 space-x-2">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
<span class="text-xs font-medium text-primary">Guardado automático</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-6">
<div class="relative">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-emerald-900/40">notifications</span>
<span class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-2 h-2 bg-secondary rounded-full"></span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-3 pl-6 border-l border-outline-variant/20">
<div class="text-right">
<p class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-900">Energy Architect</p>
<p class="text-[10px] text-emerald-600/60 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest">Level 4 Auditor</p>
</div>
<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high overflow-hidden">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="professional headshot of a male energy engineer in a modern workspace with natural lighting" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBDSa1zuHSmZMuna1ogSz5l9WohbSpYDMgWQ5sJAdvIa-Ept0RL-agPFLa6Ir6cBsxO9PZI_Foi4sgu79gSOP1Cf4oeVkErijX-dzSIBmoWcmaAP0_I6vusQ-84e7UmPSnIIoWe4kObxfH6gw1_SVTFbbR0iYk5VhoZ4rey2NNIiOVQObjW266UOmM6xHdH5UKxxFzIUxqr1vNOBJUvdeWkhTpil_RvEt96Gfw52ddlY6qpTlqofpyfjz98PN54T6LNfc0QyJ9FdNwe"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<section class="px-12 py-6 flex-1 max-w-6xl w-full mx-auto">
<div class="mb-12">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
<span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-on-surface-variant/60">Phase 01 / 05</span>
<span class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-secondary">Step 1: General Data</span>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-2 h-1.5 w-full">
<div class="flex-1 bg-secondary rounded-full"></div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-high rounded-full"></div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-high rounded-full"></div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-high rounded-full"></div>
<div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-high rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between mt-4">
<div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-secondary">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-secondary flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">01</div>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">General</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-on-surface-variant/40">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-surface-container-high flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">02</div>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Envelope</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-on-surface-variant/40">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-surface-container-high flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">03</div>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Systems</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-on-surface-variant/40">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-surface-container-high flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">04</div>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Emissions</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-on-surface-variant/40">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-surface-container-high flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">05</div>
<span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Finalize</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-12">
<div class="col-span-7">
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-xl shadow-[0px_12px_32px_rgba(25,28,27,0.04)]">
<div class="mb-8">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-emerald-900 mb-2">Identification &amp; Location</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Please provide the primary administrative and physical details for the asset being certified.</p>
</div>
<form class="space-y-8">
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70">Client Name</label>
<input class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-lg p-4 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all" placeholder="Full legal name or entity" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70">Cadastral Reference</label>
<div class="relative flex gap-2">
<input class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-lg p-4 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all font-mono tracking-wider" placeholder="20-digit alphanumeric code" type="text"/>
<button class="bg-secondary hover:bg-on-secondary-fixed-variant text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest transition-all flex items-center gap-2" type="button">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">bolt</span>
                                        Auto-complete
                                    </button>
</div>
<p class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant/60 italic">Fetch address and boundary data directly from the Land Registry.</p>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70">Property Address</label>
<textarea class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-lg p-4 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all resize-none" placeholder="Enter the full physical location..." rows="3"></textarea>
</div>
<div class="space-y-2">
<label class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-on-surface-variant/70">Property Type</label>
<select class="w-full bg-surface-container-high border-none rounded-lg p-4 text-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all appearance-none">
<option disabled="" selected="" value="">Select category...</option>
<option>Single-Family Residential</option>
<option>Multi-Family Residential</option>
<option>Commercial - Office</option>
<option>Commercial - Industrial</option>
<option>Public Administration</option>
</select>
</div>
</form>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-12 pb-12">
<button class="flex items-center gap-2 text-on-surface-variant/40 hover:text-on-surface font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">arrow_back</span>
                            Anterior
                        </button>
<button class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-container text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[11px] transition-all shadow-lg flex items-center gap-3">
                            Siguiente
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-span-5 space-y-6">
<div class="glass-panel p-8 rounded-xl border border-white/40 shadow-sm">
<h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-900 mb-6">Visual Verification</h4>
<div class="aspect-video w-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden relative mb-4">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-emerald-900/10 z-10"></div>
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="scenic architectural view of a minimalist wooden cabin in a lush green forest with large windows" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAPE_0Q-m_eENw5-FpVKbJ7aInehLW9_R_NuL5d70ZyC42qaKc5FGtJo4qwZJSGyotHZAOJL_Zdc_faqgYSVQ6PboULrvLa6907JKjOPLPw-Sid9WmAEPlBzZs0lMTJuQ6d0l_I3kXQkk3dN4KuzqWimw5g9ycVNxwFSvq5ULPGGY__Sdgz_iPWF4MGBUSc87_0IVspfoKTlcq6gxzLctXRgcHP8MBS8da0iRu4dFiI2di_3r_KtPt1uUVON48joyJWe7sF6Vqsz2I3"/>
</div>
<div class="space-y-3">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs">
<span class="text-on-surface-variant/60">Estimated Climate Zone</span>
<span class="font-bold text-emerald-900">D3 (Continental)</span>
</div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs">
<span class="text-on-surface-variant/60">Registry Status</span>
<span class="text-primary font-bold">Active Connection</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl">
<div class="flex items-start gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">lightbulb</span>
<div>
<h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-1">Architect's Note</h4>
<p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Ensuring the Cadastral Reference is correct will automatically populate the building's year of construction and orientation in Step 2.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<footer class="w-full border-t border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-900 bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-950 mt-auto">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center px-8 py-12 gap-4">
<div class="flex items-center space-x-6">
<span class="text-sm font-bold opacity-50 text-emerald-900">Eco-Monolith</span>
<p class="text-xs tracking-tight text-emerald-700/60">© 2024 Eco-Monolith Certification. Precise. Organic. Ethical.</p>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-8">
<a class="text-xs tracking-tight text-emerald-700/60 hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors" href="#">Privacy</a>
<a class="text-xs tracking-tight text-emerald-700/60 hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors" href="#">Terms</a>
<a class="text-xs tracking-tight text-emerald-700/60 hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors" href="#">Cookies</a>
<a class="text-xs tracking-tight text-emerald-700/60 hover:text-orange-700 transition-colors" href="#">SLA</a>
</div>
</div>
</footer>
</main>
</body></html>